              "free_text": [
                " The  number  of  delayed  neutrons  (DN)  was",
                " obtained  as the integral of DN decay spectrum (time",
                " dependent yield measured) corrected for  background,",
                " detector efficiency  and  contribution  of  (n,fiss)",
                " reactions. The  number  of  fissions   (induced   by",
                " photons and  neutrons) was evaluated using the MCNPX",
                " transport code."
